node.text:
Recently I’ve been trying out @sandandskyaus products and thought it’s time share my thoughts with you all #ad 
I’ve been using their Australian Pink Clay Mask and Tasmanian Spring Water Splash Serum and Hydration Boost Cream to treat myself to a masking session with an extra boost in hydration. 💦Check out the Reel I posted with their products ✨ Smooth, plump, hydrated skin is my goal and that's exactly what I get with Sand & Sky. 
Comment below your favourite Sand & Sky product! Mine has to be their Australian Pink Clay Mask 🤩 #Sandandsky #DeepDownUnder #Abeauty

Hi guys! I’ve been a massive fan of @poshmark for a while and now we’re collaborating to giveaway a Gucci bag for only $3+shipping! There's tons of awesome brands such as Fendi, Louis Vuitton, and many more for a deal, but follow my closet for a chance to win this bag now:

Download the app (link in stories) and create an account
Find my closet @KalaniBHilliker
Heart/like the listing of the bag
Once the listing is available, the first person to purchase wins! 
Comment below with your @poshmark closet name and let me know if you want me to do more collabs with Posh! #ad #poshaffiliate
